# console.newLine

<dl>
<dt> Instance of </dt><dd markdown="1">
 [`Function`]({{site.baseurl}}\built-ins\Function) 
</dd>
<dt> Return value </dt><dd markdown="1">
 `console` 
</dd>
</dl>

### Description

Writes the new line character or characters sequence
(platform dependent) to standard output stream.

### Example

```js
console.newLine();
```
